snippet.title: My Daughter is a Cultist Game Jam trailer
snippet.description:
Japanese Horror meets Lovecraft in this manga style game. 

Play the game (free): http://virtuaworlds.itch.io

Premise: YOU'RE JUST A NORMAL GUY TRYING TO GET SOME SLEEP. YOU HEAR A BUMP IN THE NIGHT.
WHAT WAS THAT? WHY IS YOUR DAUGHTER ACTING SO WEIRD? 
IS IT PARENTHOOD OR A HORRIBLE CURIOSITY THAT COMPELS YOU TO FIND OUT?
